title.rendered: 10th Annual SXSW EDU Conference and Festival

content.rendered:
Now in its 10th year, the SXSW EDU® Conference and Festival cultivates and empowers a community of engaged stakeholders to advance teaching and learning. The annual four-day event affords registrants open access to engaging sessions, immersive workshops, interactive learning experiences, film screenings, early-stage startups, business opportunities, and networking.

SXSW EDU is a component of the South by Southwest® family of conferences and festivals that has grown from 800 to over 8,000 registrants in the last decade. Join the passionate and innovative community at SXSW EDU, March 9-12, 2020 in Austin, Texas.

An opportunity that only happens once in a lifetime. Don’t miss it
